title: League of Legends Bundesliga by Dirtyboy49

embed.description: Hello Guys, I wanna start a new Tournament for fun! We play 5vs5 Draft Pick at Summoners Rift. You need min. 6 players...

body: I wanna start a Tournament for Fun in a league system. I hope we will get prizes from League of Legends Support for the Tournament. Max Lvl. Gold! The Tournament starts at Saturday 28.03.2015! It's a Tournamanet for the low elo!
